<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>로그인</title>
        <script src="/login.mjs" type="module"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/login.css" />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="login-form">
                <h1 class="title">로그인</h1>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        name="id"
                        placeholder="아이디"
                        required="required"
                    />
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                        account_circle
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <input
                        type="password"
                        name="password"
                        placeholder="비밀번호"
                        required="required"
                    />
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined"> lock </span>
                    <div class="visibility-container">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="visibility">
                            visibility
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined"
                            id="visibility-off"
                            style="display: none"
                        >
                            visibility_off
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="login-button" type="submit" />
                <label for="login-button">로그인</label>
            </div>
            <div class="util-container">
                <div class="remember-me-container">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="remember-me" />
                    <label for="remember-me"></label>
                    <label for="remember-me">
                        <span>나를 기억하기</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="find-password-container">
                    <a class="find-password" href="/find-password"
                        >비밀번호 찾기</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <div class="register-container">
                <span class="register-link-text"
                    >아직 계정이 없으십니까? |
                    <a class="register-link" href="/register">회원가입</a></span
                >
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="notice-container" />
    </body>
</html>
